{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO419865B0529P0D1N000029", "chronotag": "1739874684337", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "CD29", "numeroOrdreDepot": "29", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "CION-DVP", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO419865B0529P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PRJLANR5L17B0529", "triAmendement": "noaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaai", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA841131", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845401", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"acteurRef": ["PA720668", "PA841761", "PA841621", "PA841451", "PA793632", "PA842085", "PA796026", "PA841587", "PA794530", "PA840837", "PA793852", "PA794894", "PA841575"]}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "Mme&#160;Bouquin,  M.&#160;Blairy, M.&#160;Dutremble, M.&#160;Evrard, M.&#160;Guibert, M.&#160;Houssin, M.&#160;Humbert, Mme&#160;Lechanteux, M.&#160;David&#160;Magnier, M.&#160;Marchio, M.&#160;Markowsky, M.&#160;Meurin, Mme&#160;Sabatini et M.&#160;Vos"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article 38", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 38", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 38", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/0529.asp#D_Article_38"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"avant_A_Apres": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "numero": "16", "alineaDesignation": "Alin\u00e9a 16"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00C0; la derni&#x00E8;re phrase de l&#x2019;alin&#x00E9;a&nbsp;16, substituer aux mots&nbsp;:</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;peut mettre&nbsp;&#x00BB;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">le mot&nbsp;:</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;met&nbsp;&#x00BB;.</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>&nbsp;</p><p>Cet amendement pr&#x00E9;cise que l&#x2019;&#x00E9;limination des conteneurs non rechargeables de gaz &#x00E0; effet de serre fluor&#x00E9; sera imput&#x00E9;e aux acteurs responsables, &#x00E0; savoir l&#x2019;importateur, le distributeur ou l&#x2019;exportateur.</p><p>L&#x2019;objectif est clair : &#x00E9;viter que les co&#x00FB;ts li&#x00E9;s au non-respect de la r&#x00E9;glementation par des industriels ne soient support&#x00E9;s par les finances publiques. Cette mesure assure une responsabilisation directe des acteurs &#x00E9;conomiques, en coh&#x00E9;rence avec le principe du pollueur-payeur.</p><p>En renfor&#x00E7;ant ainsi la responsabilit&#x00E9; des diff&#x00E9;rents intervenants de la cha&#x00EE;ne, cet amendement garantit une application rigoureuse de la loi tout en pr&#x00E9;servant les finances publiques de charges indues.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2024-11-22", "datePublication": "2024-11-27", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Rejet\u00e9"}}, "dateSort": "2024-11-27T12:38:11+01:00", "sort": "Rejet\u00e9"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO419865B0529P0D1N000029?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}